This page on SteamDB lists all the games tagged as 'Party-Based RPG'. Party-based RPGs are role-playing games that allow players to form a party of characters, each with unique abilities and roles. These games emphasize teamwork, cooperation, and strategy as players navigate quests, battles, and storylines together. Party members may have different classes, skills, or strengths, requiring effective communication and coordination to overcome challenges. Players can manage their party composition and develop relationships between characters. Party-Based RPGs offer a rich and immersive gaming experience that encourages social interaction, collaboration, and replayability.
